---
title: Cannellini & Eggplant Potato Top Pie with Balsamic Salad & Flaked Almonds
description: This easy to make veggie deluxe pie is a taste sensation. Roasted eggplant, seasoned cannellini beans and veggies hidden under
a blanket of mashed potatoes is already a great dinner, but bake it into a pie and serve with toasted almonds on a balsamic salad
and dinner just become a lot more exciting!

